ZH: 1. 请愿书已经提交给政府部门了。
EN: The petition has been submitted to the government department.
ZH: 2. 我们正在请愿以争取更多的保护自然资源。
EN: We are petitioning for more protection of natural resources.
ZH: 3. 他发起了一个请愿运动，要求停止动物园的建设。
EN: He initiated a petition campaign to stop the construction of the zoo.
ZH: 4. 我们需要更多的签名来支持我们的请愿。
EN: We need more signatures to support our petition.
ZH: 5. 学生们请愿要求增加课外活动的时间。
EN: The students are petitioning to increase the extra-curricular activities time.
ZH: 6. 签署这份请愿书是你对环保事业的支持。
EN: Signing this petition shows your support for environmental conservation.
ZH: 7. 这个请愿活动得到了大部分居民的支持。
EN: This petition campaign has gained support from a majority of residents.
ZH: 8. 这个请愿已经得到了市长的回应。
EN: This petition has received a response from the mayor.
ZH: 9. 请愿者们在市中心集会以表达他们的要求。
EN: The petitioners gathered in the city center to express their demands.
ZH: 10. 这个请愿书上有人们对食品安全问题的关注。
EN: The petition contains people's concerns about food safety issues.
ZH: 11. 她通过在线请愿网站发起了一项关于教育改革的请愿。
EN: She initiated a petition on an online platform regarding educational reforms.
ZH: 12. 同学们集体请愿要求提供更好的体育设施。
EN: The classmates petitioned collectively to demand better sports facilities.
ZH: 13. 这个请愿书的目的是呼吁政府减少污染。
EN: The purpose of this petition is to urge the government to reduce pollution.
ZH: 14. 我们计划发起一次关于普通公民权益的请愿活动。
EN: We are planning to initiate a petition campaign regarding the rights of ordinary citizens.
ZH: 15. 请愿者们在市政厅外集会以传达他们的意愿。
EN: The petitioners gathered outside the city hall to convey their intentions.
ZH: 16. 这些签名是我们请愿的证明。
EN: These signatures are proof of our petition.
ZH: 17. 这个请愿活动得到了媒体的关注。
EN: This petition campaign has gained media attention.
ZH: 18. 这个请愿书上有几千人签名了。
EN: Several thousand people have signed this petition.
ZH: 19. 我们希望政府能积极回应我们的请愿。
EN: We hope the government will respond actively to our petition.
ZH: 20. 我的邻居们组织了一个请愿运动以改善社区的环境问题。
EN: My neighbors organized a petition campaign to address environmental issues in the community.
